=== Pronunciation ===
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /'/
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /'ʃeɪk/

=== Transitive verb ===

'''to shake''' ([[shook]], [[shaken]])

# to cause (something) to move rapidly from side to side.  (''The earthquake shook the building.'')
# to move (something) [[rapid]]ly from side to side, especially to mix it.
# to remove (something) by moving it vigorously. (''The dog shook the water from its fur.'')
# to [[shock]].  (''Her father's death shook her terribly.'')
# to [[lose]], [[evade]], or [[get rid of]] (something) (''I can't shake the feeling that I forgot something.'')

